text: Nabi muminadera nikata tadera nijedera apeksa adhika ghanistha ebam tamra strigana tadera mata. Allahara bidhana anuyayi mumina o muhajiraganera madhye yara atniya, tara paraspare adhika ghanistha. Tabe tomara yadi tomadera bandhudera prati daya-daksinya karate ca'o, karate para. Eta la'ohe-mahaphuye likhita ache.
